        <h2>A Legacy of Craftsmanship</h2>
        <p>CNO Pole Barns was founded in 1970 in Clarkston, Michigan, with a simple mission: build high-quality structures at fair prices. What began as a small family operation has grown into one of Southeast Michigan's most trusted construction companies.</p>
        <p>For over 55 years, we've built everything from simple storage barns to complex equestrian facilities and modern barndominiums. Every project gets the same level of dedication, whether it's a one-car garage or a 10,000 sq ft commercial building.</p>
        <p>Today, under the leadership of owner Zosim Serban, CNO continues the tradition of quality craftsmanship, honest communication, and building relationships that last as long as our structures.</p>
      </div>
